{"article_id":"lv0ZtqsoBcr2vMxP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Tuesday defended the controversial $ 1 trillion-plus budget deal","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"heading for a vote","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"-","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"as he and congressional Republicans face conservative anger at what critics see as a cave to Democrats on everything from sanctuary cities to funding for Planned Parenthood .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"\" The reason for the plan","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"negotiated between the Republicans and Democrats","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"is that we need 60 votes in the Senate","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"which are not there ! \"","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Trump tweeted ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"adding","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that the solution is to elect more Republican senators in 2018","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"`` or change the rules '' of the Senate filibuster .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The reason for the plan","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"negotiated between the Republicans and Democrats","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"is that we need 60 votes in the Senate","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"which are not there !","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"We ....","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"May 2 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"either elect more Republican Senators in 2018","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"or change the rules now to 51 % .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Our country needs a good `` shutdown '' in September","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"to fix mess !","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"May 2 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"He added a warning shot :","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"`` Our country needs a good 'shutdown ' in September","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to fix mess ! ''","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Republican and Democratic lawmakers made the budget deal ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"announced Monday ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"in order to fund the government through September","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"and avoid a shutdown later this week .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"despite Republicans controlling the House , Senate and White House ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"the deal is widely perceived as benefiting Democratic interests and priorities ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"while sidelining some of the items on Trump 's wishlist .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Heritage Action , an outside conservative group , on Tuesday urged a `` no '' vote on the package ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"with Heritage Foundation analysts claiming","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"it `` woefully fails the test of fiscal responsibility","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and does not advance important conservative policies . ''","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"The plan has no funding for Trump ' s much vaunted border wall ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"though it includes $ 1.5 billion for border security .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"While the deal does include an increase in military spending","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"as requested by Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"it does not reduce funding for so-called \" sanctuary cities \"","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"- jurisdictions","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"that refuse to comply with federal immigration law -","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"and continues to fund abortion provider Planned Parenthood .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Non-defense spending also sees an increase ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"and Democrats managed to kill 160 Republican riders on issues such as environmental regulations .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"The deal also includes a $ 2 billion increase in spending for the National Institutes of Health .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"At a White House ceremony","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"to award a trophy to the Air Force football team ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Trump again hailed parts of the deal ,","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"it secured the `` single largest increase in border security funding in 10 years ''","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"and noted","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"that it broke the Obama-era `` parity rule ''","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"-- that every increase in military spending must be matched by an increase in domestic spending .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"`` That 's not happening any more ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"I can tell you ...","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"you 're going to have the money","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"we need","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"and the equipment","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"we need , ''","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"`` Our military is going to be taken care of ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that I promise you . ''","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"But Democrats reacted with glee to a supposed victory","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"pulled out of the embers of a brutal November election defeat .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"we had a strategy","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"and it worked , \"","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Senate Democratic Leader Chuck Schumer , D-N.Y. , said in an interview with The Washington Post .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"\" Democrats and Republicans in the House and Senate were closer to one another","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"than Republicans were to Donald Trump . \"","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Conservatives took to media outlets and TV","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"to express their anger ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"aimed particularly at congressional Republicans and House Speaker Paul Ryan , R-Wis .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"\" DEMS CELEBRATE 'REPUBLICAN ' BUDGET ! \"","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"declared the top headline on the Drudge Report Tuesday morning ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"accompanied by a grinning picture of House Democratic Leader Nancy Pelosi , D-Calif.","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Another headline read :","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"\" MORE PAGES THAN OBAMA STIMULUS \"","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"\" We do not have a Republican Party on Capitol Hill","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"that can get its act together , \"","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Fox News contributor Laura Ingraham said on `` Fox & Friends '' Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"\" I don ' t know","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"how you would carry water for this , ''","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"conservative talk show host Rush Limbaugh said Monday .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"`` Not that I want to ;","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"don ' t misunderstand .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"I ' m just coming up with new ways","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"to explain","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"what a sellout , disaster , betrayal","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"- whatever you want to call this -","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"it is . ''","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"At a House GOP leadership press conference Tuesday morning , however , Speaker Ryan and other top Republicans defended the package .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Ryan touted the \" down payment on border security \"","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"and dismissed what he called Democrats ' \" PR machine \"","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"playing up their end of the bargain .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"\" Don ' t look at the press releases ,","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"look at the bill , \"","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"Ryan said ,","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"adding","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"there are \" a lot of conservative wins here . \"","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"Majority Whip Steve Scalise , R-La. , touted pay raises for military service members and cuts to \" areas","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"where we ' ve seen government run out of control \" like the EPA .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Members of the House Freedom Caucus predicted conservative opposition in Congress .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"`` Money goes to Planned Parenthood ,","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"as you said .","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"Money continues to go to sanctuary cities ,","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"but no money for the border wall , ''","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"Rep. Jim Jordan , R-Ohio , said in an interview with CNN .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"you 're going to see a lot of conservatives against this plan this week . ''","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"Even before Trump ' s tweets , some Republicans looked to defend the bill .","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"They noted","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"that Trump got the defense spending priorities","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"he asked for ,","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"while pointing to other victories such as no new money for Puerto Rico ' s Medicaid program , a 50 percent increase for abstinence education , increased funding in the fight against opioid addiction , and another cut for the EPA ' s budget .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"White House Press Secretary Sean Spicer noted","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"that the deal includes $ 1.5 billion","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"secured for enhanced border security and detention capabilities ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"and called it a \" down payment \" on the border wall ,","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"which","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"he reiterated","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"is going to get built during Trump ' s time in office .","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"`` Make no mistake ,","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"the wall is going to be built , ''","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"`` We have five months left in this fiscal year ,","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"we 're getting $ 1.52 billion for border security ,","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"there 's a lot","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"that can be done with that . ''","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"But some conservatives say","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"passing a bill","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"funding Democratic priorities","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"will hurt Republicans down the road in the 2018 midterms .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"\" I find this to be so demoralizing , disappointing","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"and I think","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"they ' re going to have hell to pay for this budget , \"","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"Ingraham said .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"The bill is expected to go to the House floor Wednesday , and to the Senate Thursday , ahead of the shutdown deadline on Friday .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":291,"left":290,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":175,"right":289,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":149,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":148,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":147,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":156,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":153,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":150,"right":151,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":9,"right":154,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":173,"left":165,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":163,"right":164,"relation":"sa